Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.35,NOTES 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HF1F1F1&\blur0.8\bord0\1a&H64&\frz11.75\move(676,600,680,222,25,2361)}各位同学请节约用水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.81,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,トイレ　どうするっす
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.81,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,厕所怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嘘　トイレ禁止？
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.44,0:03:28.31,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不会吧 难道不准用了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.75,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,トイレ流すの海水だから
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.75,0:03:30.75,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,冲厕所用的是海水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ああ　そっか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.02,0:03:32.25,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:35.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,あんなにトイレットペーパー買い込んだのに
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.72,0:03:35.92,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,买了那么多卫生纸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.25,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,誰か　塩水使ったのは
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.25,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,是谁放的盐水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.84,TEXT-JP-UP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,出てこい　誰か
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.65,0:03:44.84,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,给我出来 到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.83,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,忘れてた
Dialogue: 1,0:03:42.97,0:03:44.83,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,クロちゃんの話　聞いた
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.85,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你听说小黑那件事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.38,0:03:48.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ウイ
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.38,0:03:48.98,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,听了
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.33,TEXT-CN @方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs70\c&H383838&\move(796,296,796,386)\frz276.1}今天开始淋浴与泡澡
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.33,TEXT-CN @方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,{\fs70\bord0\c&H383838&\frz271.7\move(620,378,620,468)}将使用海水
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.95,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,三日ぶりなのに　洗うべきか
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.54,0:03:55.95,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,三天没洗了 洗是不洗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.65,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,何じゃ　その頭は
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.75,0:04:00.65,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你们的头发怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.21,0:04:03.23,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,見事に爆発しちゃったね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.21,0:04:03.23,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,就像爆炸头一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:08.89,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,髪は女の命ですよね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.71,0:04:08.89,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,头发可是女孩子的命根
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,キラキラ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:11.72,0:04:12.72,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,あれ　何で
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.89,0:04:14.17,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,咦 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.15,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,知るか
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.24,0:04:15.15,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,鬼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,鯖の水煮にトマトの水煮
Dialogue: 1,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.82,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,水煮鲭鱼 水煮番茄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ミックスベジタブルに乾パン
Dialogue: 1,0:04:20.16,0:04:22.16,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,什锦蔬菜 压缩饼干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.09,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,見事な缶詰料理じゃな
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.57,0:04:25.09,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,一堆罐装食品 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.81,0:04:26.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,贅沢言わない
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.81,0:04:26.96,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,别那么挑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,まっ　しょうがないよ　食べよう
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.26,0:04:29.63,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,唉 没办法 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,一雨降らねぇかなぁ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.82,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,要是下场雨就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,もう限界だよ
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.24,0:04:34.51,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我快到极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,どうしよう
Dialogue: 1,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.59,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,パンツが塩の香りって嫌だよね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:37.08,0:04:39.92,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,真不想让内裤沾上海水的咸味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,何かね
Dialogue: 1,0:04:40.52,0:04:41.45,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,炭酸ダメなの　シロ…
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.72,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你不爱喝碳酸饮料吗 小…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長
Dialogue: 1,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.48,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,あ…あの　もうすぐ霧の中に入ります
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.61,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,呃 那个 前方有雾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,サトちゃん　探照灯お願い
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.74,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,小聪 打开探照灯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ココちゃん　霧笛鳴らして
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.48,0:05:07.50,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,小幸 鸣雾笛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雨だ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.24,0:05:17.32,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,下雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私も手伝うよ
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.92,0:05:57.13,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雨水溜めるどころじゃないぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:03.44,0:06:05.63,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这样根本没法收集雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,痛い
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.84,0:06:07.18,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.89,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,すべる
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.89,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,太滑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,せっかく溜めた水が…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.95,0:06:11.66,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,好不容易才接到一点雨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,撤収っす　撤収
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.71,0:06:13.02,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,撤退 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,大低気圧っす
Dialogue: 1,0:06:13.40,0:06:16.96,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这是个大型低气压
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長　お話が…
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.64,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,舰长 借一步说话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:32.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,荒天につき　上甲板の通行禁止します
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.15,0:06:32.51,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,暴雨天气 禁止前往上层甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.85,TEXT-JP-UP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,繰り返します　上甲板の通行禁止
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.85,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,重复一遍 禁止前往上层甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,上　通れないと不便だね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.61,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不能走甲板还真是不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,今日のご飯何だろう　お腹空いた
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.63,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,今天的晚饭是什么呢 我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:41.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,どうぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.20,0:06:41.92,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你先请
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,サンキュー
Dialogue: 1,0:06:41.98,0:06:43.17,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.83,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ごめんね
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.52,0:06:46.83,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.03,0:06:50.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,よいしょ
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.03,0:06:50.88,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,真挤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,すごい
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.52,0:06:57.87,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,好响啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.65,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,岬さん　どうかしたの
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.86,0:07:01.65,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,岬同学 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.39,0:07:04.09,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ちょっと
Dialogue: 1,0:07:03.39,0:07:04.09,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.81,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ごめん　私もう…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.81,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,当直代わってもらってくる
Dialogue: 1,0:07:09.72,0:07:11.20,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我去找个人代班
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,嫌だ　かっこいい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.46,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不要啊 帅死我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私のおマッチにななななんのこと…
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.33,0:07:24.17,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你对我家真知知做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.28,0:07:25.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.28,0:07:25.04,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,舰长？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:24.99,TEXT-JP-UP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,落ち着いて
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.36,0:07:24.99,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,冷静一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,それが落ち着いていられるか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.16,0:07:27.32,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你叫我怎么冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,成敗いたす　そこになおれ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:27.45,0:07:30.22,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我要办了她 你给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,わしは吾の命もらう
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.04,0:07:33.04,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,要拿下你的命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.75,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「眉毛抜くんも」
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.75,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「跟拔蛀牙一样」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「同じことなんで」
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.75,0:07:36.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「轻而易举」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ここええよな
Dialogue: 1,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.69,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这句真是经典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,激しく同意であります
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.74,0:07:39.28,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,非常之赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,どうして私の部屋で見るんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.71,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么要在我房间看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私の部屋にテレビないんで
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.49,0:07:44.72,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我房间没电视
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長も見るか
Dialogue: 1,0:07:44.72,0:07:46.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长你看不看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,いい
Dialogue: 1,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,免了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ここじゃここ
Dialogue: 1,0:07:48.06,0:07:49.28,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,就是这一段啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長　夜分にすみません
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.87,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长 这么晚打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,何です
Dialogue: 1,0:07:55.32,0:07:56.24,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,悪いんだけど　当直代わってもらえる
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.01,0:08:00.49,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不好意思 能代我班吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「どしたんなら」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.12,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「咋了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:03.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「言うてみ」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.22,0:08:03.12,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「张嘴说话啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ちょっとすごくて…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:04.40,0:08:05.69,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,外边太响了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.67,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「何がじゃ」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.67,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「什么」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「言うてみ」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.67,0:08:07.63,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「张嘴说话啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雷
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.32,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,雷声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:14.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「ほうか　分かった」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.29,0:08:14.27,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「是吗 没办法」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「ほいじゃ　行ってくるけぇの」
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.91,0:08:17.26,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「咱去去就回」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,「風下には立たんけえ」　バサァ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.74,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,「岂能轻易拜了下风」 哗啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:30.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,そろそろ寝たいんですが
Dialogue: 1,0:08:28.12,0:08:30.28,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我很困了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,そんなに雷が怖いのか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:30.81,0:08:32.97,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你这么怕打雷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.23,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雷はへそを取ったりせんぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.23,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,雷公又不会偷走肚脐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.23,NOTES 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,注：日本传说雷公会偷走小孩的肚脐。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,雷が怖いっていうか
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.53,0:08:37.60,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我怕的不是打雷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:38.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　何だ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.90,0:08:38.85,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,那是怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.07,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ただ…
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.35,0:08:43.07,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,思い出すから
Dialogue: 1,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.34,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,会想起过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.56,0:08:54.73,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,乗客の皆様　本船は只今救難信号を発信中です
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.56,0:08:54.73,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,各位乘客 本船已发送求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:58.03,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,まもなく　ブルーマーメード隊がやってくるまでの間
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.12,0:08:58.03,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,在蓝色人鱼赶来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.95,TEXT-JP-UP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,もう水が来てるから　早くしろ
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.95,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,水涨上来了 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.24,0:09:01.15,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,落ち着いて　誘導員の指示に従ってください
Dialogue: 1,0:08:58.24,0:09:01.15,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,请保持冷静 听从救援人员的指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.52,TEXT-JP-UP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,急げよ
Dialogue: 1,0:09:00.49,0:09:01.52,TEXT-CN-UP 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.21,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お母さん　痛い
Dialogue: 1,0:09:03.71,0:09:05.21,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,妈妈 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.09,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,明乃　早く海に飛び込みなさい
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.61,0:09:08.09,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,明乃 快点跳下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,急いで
Dialogue: 1,0:09:08.56,0:09:09.37,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お父さんとお母さんは
Dialogue: 1,0:09:09.72,0:09:11.28,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.28,0:09:11.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,早く
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.28,0:09:11.88,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お父さん…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.45,0:09:18.27,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.77,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お母さんは　なんでいないの
Dialogue: 1,0:09:19.10,0:09:21.77,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,妈妈呢 他们怎么不在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,なんで
Dialogue: 1,0:09:24.19,0:09:25.04,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:31.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お父さん　お母さん
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.48,0:09:31.64,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.48,0:09:35.74,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私がもっと早く飛び込んでたら
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.48,0:09:35.74,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,要是我能早点跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:40.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お父さんもお母さんも…　もしかしたら…
Dialogue: 1,0:09:36.60,0:09:40.72,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈或许就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長　救難信号です
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.73,0:09:42.51,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,舰长 有求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救難信号ってどこから？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.22,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,谁发出的求救信号
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.35,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,新橋商店街船です
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.57,0:09:48.35,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,新桥商店街船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:52.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全長135メートル　総トン数14000
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.91,0:09:52.46,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,全长135m 总吨位14000t
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:56.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,現在左に傾斜し　船内に浸水している模様
Dialogue: 1,0:09:52.62,0:09:56.01,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,左舷倾侧 好像是进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,乗員は
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.37,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,乘员有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全乗員552名　現在避難中だとのことです
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.72,0:10:01.28,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,总乘员552名 现在正在避难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,近くの船は？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.28,0:10:02.48,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,附近还有船吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,我々が一番近いです
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.59,0:10:04.40,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们距离最近
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.18,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ブルーマー本隊に連絡して　学校にも
Dialogue: 1,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.18,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,联系蓝人总部和学校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:07.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:10:07.18,0:10:07.90,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.91,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,こちら航洋艦晴風　艦長の岬明乃です
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.76,0:10:12.91,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我是航海舰晴风号舰长 岬明乃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,こちらは新橋　ファラウレップ南東13マイル地点
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.76,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们是新桥 在法拉洛普岛东南13海里处
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:22.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,航行中に暗礁に乗り上げました　坐礁時刻は15分前
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.24,0:10:22.33,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,15分钟前 在航行时撞上了暗礁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,現在も船体中央部が触底しています
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.07,0:10:25.82,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在船体中央依然挂在暗礁上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:26.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,怪我人は？
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.04,0:10:26.96,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,有人受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,軽傷者が十名
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.13,0:10:28.46,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,十人轻伤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.77,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,浸水はありますか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.46,0:10:29.77,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,进水了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,左舷側はあると思われます
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.03,0:10:31.98,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,左舷应该是进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,火災は発生していますか
Dialogue: 1,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.71,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,起火了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,まだ確認しておりません
Dialogue: 1,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.31,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:39.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,了解しました　そちらまでの到達時間は約五十分
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.47,0:10:39.61,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,明白了 我舰大约50分钟后可以抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.67,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,それまで船長は避難誘導を続けてください
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.82,0:10:42.67,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,在那之前请船长您继续引导避难
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,リンちゃん　急いで
Dialogue: 1,0:10:43.21,0:10:44.62,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,小铃 加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.41,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,りょ…了解
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.41,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.77,0:10:48.83,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,達する
Dialogue: 1,0:10:47.77,0:10:48.83,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,全体听令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ウルシー環礁に座礁船発見
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.12,0:10:51.53,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,乌利西环礁附近有船只触礁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.63,0:10:54.81,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,本艦はこれより当該船舶の救助に向かいます
Dialogue: 1,0:10:51.63,0:10:54.81,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,本舰将前往营救此船
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,海難救助用意
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.26,0:10:56.76,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,准备海难救援
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:01.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,砲雷科と航海科で手のあいてる人は準備を急いで
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.36,0:11:01.02,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,炮雷科及航海科的非执勤人员请立即开始准备
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,大変　大変
Dialogue: 1,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.56,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,糟啦糟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ビビるっす
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.80,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,吓死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.38,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,きつい
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.38,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,好紧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,太った？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.38,0:11:09.37,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,胖了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,太っちゃったかな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.16,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,天気晴朗なれども波高し
Dialogue: 1,0:11:12.78,0:11:15.32,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,天气晴朗 不过风大浪高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.43,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,晴れたな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.43,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,风暴过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,低気圧は西に移動した模様です
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.92,0:11:19.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,低气压往西边去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,傾きは40度くらいか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.26,0:11:21.05,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,倾斜角度约为40度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:24.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,50度を越えると転覆する危険が高まるぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.37,0:11:24.22,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,超过50度时很可能就会倾覆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,新橋の船内図です
Dialogue: 1,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.40,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这是新桥的船内地图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:30.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,三階吹き抜けてて商店　四階が居住区
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.80,0:11:30.14,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,前三层都是商店 四层是居住分区
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,中央がブリッジになってます
Dialogue: 1,0:11:30.78,0:11:32.36,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,中央是舰桥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救助準備は完了した
Dialogue: 1,0:11:35.48,0:11:36.94,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,做好救援准备了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.15,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,準備OKです
Dialogue: 1,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.15,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,准备就绪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,それと私もスキッパー…
Dialogue: 1,0:11:39.47,0:11:41.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也开跳艇…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,また艦長が持ち場を離れる気か
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.53,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你这个舰长又打算擅离职守吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,何ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:11:44.97,0:11:45.93,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,こういう時　艦長ってどうしたらいいのかな
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.45,0:11:50.60,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,作为舰长 这种时候该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私に聞かないでください
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.50,0:11:53.16,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,别问我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,分かんなくなっちゃって
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.36,0:11:54.84,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我有点不明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長は船にいてください
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.32,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,舰长就待在船上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救助隊の指揮は？
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.87,0:11:59.20,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,谁去指挥救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私がやります
Dialogue: 1,0:12:00.24,0:12:01.87,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,わしも行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.87,0:12:02.99,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,老夫也去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,分かった　私はここから指示を送るね
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.62,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,好 那我在船上指挥你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:15.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私とミーナさん　砲雷科三名で船内に入る
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.85,0:12:15.13,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我 明娜 加上炮雷科的三个人登船
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:18.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ダイバー隊は海に潜って　船体の損傷を確認
Dialogue: 1,0:12:15.34,0:12:18.44,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,潜水队入海确认船体受损情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.76,0:12:22.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,航海科と応急員は救命ボートに乗っている乗員を晴風に誘導
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.76,0:12:22.84,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,航海科与急救员引导登上救生艇的人去晴风号
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.13,0:12:23.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:12:23.13,0:12:23.90,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救助訓練は中学で散々やったけど
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.22,0:12:27.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,初中时就接受过无数次救援训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,実践は初めてとなぁ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.94,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不过实际操作还是头一回
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.67,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ちゃんとできるかな
Dialogue: 1,0:12:29.07,0:12:30.67,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,能做好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:31.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,大丈夫だ
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.84,0:12:31.84,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,平気平気
Dialogue: 1,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.04,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,放心放心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:37.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私は運が悪いんだけど　大丈夫だろうか
Dialogue: 1,0:12:33.96,0:12:37.12,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我总是不走运 不会出问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,空気読め
Dialogue: 1,0:12:39.80,0:12:41.13,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,说话要看场合
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,探照灯照射始め
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.04,0:12:43.80,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,点亮探照灯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.62,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.80,0:12:54.54,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,現…現場に到着しました
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.38,0:12:58.26,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我…我们已经抵达现场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,甲板は人で溢れています
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.64,0:13:00.51,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,甲板上都是人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,甲板は応急員に任せて
Dialogue: 1,0:13:00.62,0:13:02.27,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,甲板交给急救员
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,船内の生存者を確認して
Dialogue: 1,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.14,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,去搜救船内的幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救助　開始
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.94,0:13:06.44,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,开始救援
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救助どうなってんだよ
Dialogue: 1,0:13:06.64,0:13:08.17,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,救援的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ま…先ずは人数の確認よね
Dialogue: 1,0:13:08.99,0:13:11.53,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,首…首先应该清点人数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,リストバンドリストバンド
Dialogue: 1,0:13:11.53,0:13:13.28,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,识别手环呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,先に怪我人の確認じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.31,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,应该先清点伤患吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.53,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,マニュアル持って来ればよかった
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.27,0:13:18.53,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,要是带指导手册来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.97,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,晴風副長宗谷ましろです
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.86,0:13:20.97,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我是晴风号副舰长宗谷真白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ただいまから船内確認に入ります
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.55,0:13:23.46,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在开始搜救船内幸存者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.84,0:13:28.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,居住区はまだ乗員が残っている模様です　よろしくお願いします
Dialogue: 1,0:13:23.84,0:13:28.01,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,居住分区好像还有人 麻烦各位了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,スプリンクラーが作動していない
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.98,0:13:50.14,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,洒水器没有反应
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,非常用システムがやられちゃったってこと？
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.86,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,应急系统被撞坏了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ってことは
Dialogue: 1,0:13:53.29,0:13:54.40,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,この船って…
Dialogue: 1,0:13:54.96,0:13:56.59,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这艘船…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:14:01.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,船体は第四区画前百二十メートルに渡って亀裂が入っており
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.12,0:14:01.52,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,船体四号分区前约有一百二十米长的裂纹
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,前方三区画が浸水している模様ですわ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.46,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,前面的三个分区好像已经进水了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:09.55,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,こちら宗谷　新橋の非常用システムが動作不良を起こしている
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.31,0:14:09.55,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我是宗谷 新桥的紧急系统出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.08,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,何かあったんですか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.77,0:14:11.08,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,分からない　でも…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.21,0:14:13.04,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我不知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,新橋に接舷する　急いで
Dialogue: 1,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.52,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,立刻与新桥接舷 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.29,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,りょ…了解
Dialogue: 1,0:14:15.88,0:14:17.29,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,環礁に気をつけて　急いで中の人たちを甲板へ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.72,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,注意避开环礁 立刻把船上的人引导到甲板上去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,早く上へ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:21.00,0:14:22.24,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,去甲板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,急げ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:22.88,0:14:23.64,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,乗員　まもなく避難を終えます
Dialogue: 1,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.14,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,避难引导马上就能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:27.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 1,0:14:27.21,0:14:27.90,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,多聞丸がいないんです
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.86,0:14:30.59,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,多闻丸不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,気がついたら側にいなくて
Dialogue: 1,0:14:31.72,0:14:33.39,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,回过神来的时候就不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,まだ小さい子ですか
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.82,0:14:35.37,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,他还很小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.56,0:14:36.28,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.43,0:14:40.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,捜索してないのは第五区画飲食店街部分だわ
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.43,0:14:40.01,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,还没搜查的只有五号分区饮食街了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,よし　行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.60,0:14:41.98,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,好 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.56,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,多聞丸ちゃんは任せて　お二人は避難を
Dialogue: 1,0:14:42.92,0:14:45.56,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们去找多闻丸 你们先去避难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,こちらです
Dialogue: 1,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.14,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这边走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.28,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,乗員の避難は終了しました
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.28,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,避难引导成功结束
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.63,0:14:54.65,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,中に入った救助隊も船から出てきたそうです
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.63,0:14:54.65,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,进去的救援队也都出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:15:00.04,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,でも　副長とミーナさんが船尾方向の捜索に向かったと報告が
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.72,0:15:00.04,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,但是副舰长和明娜同学好像还在船尾方面继续搜救
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.52,0:15:04.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小さいお子さんが一人行方不明だそうで
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.52,0:15:04.36,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,据说有个小孩不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私はこっちを探してみる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:05.36,0:15:07.02,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我去找这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,じゃあわしはあっちを
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.26,0:15:08.62,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,老夫找那边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.44,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,多聞丸
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.44,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,多闻丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.02,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,小さい子って
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.15,0:15:21.02,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,他还很小…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,子猫のことか
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.52,0:15:23.16,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,原来说的是猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.67,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,やば　すぎる
Dialogue: 1,0:15:37.02,0:15:38.67,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.35,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,大変ところじゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.35,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,大事不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長　新橋が
Dialogue: 1,0:15:40.35,0:15:42.06,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,舰长 新桥要沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.23,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,もやいを解いて
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.22,0:15:43.23,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,解开称人结
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,全速離脱
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.64,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,全速撤离
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,真っ二つじゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.62,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,彻底断两半了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長　まだ中に副長とミーナさんがいるそうです
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.58,0:15:52.31,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,舰长 副舰长和明娜同学好像还在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,えらいこっちゃ　えらいこっちゃ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.41,0:15:54.60,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,事情大条了 事情大条了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.06,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,いた　あそこ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:54.88,0:15:56.06,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,找到了 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ミーナちゃん　こっちよ
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.64,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,小娜 来这边
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.84,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ミーナ　早く逃げて
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.03,0:15:59.84,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,明娜 跑快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.21,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,逃げとるんじゃい
Dialogue: 1,0:15:59.84,0:16:01.21,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,老夫不正跑着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.39,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,よろしいですから　飛び込んでください
Dialogue: 1,0:16:01.21,0:16:03.39,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们减速 你跳下来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.61,0:16:06.16,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長　副長　聞こえる
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.61,0:16:06.16,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长 副舰长 听得见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.83,0:16:07.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.83,0:16:07.60,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,请讲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,船体の中央部分で裂けたの
Dialogue: 1,0:16:07.74,0:16:09.71,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,船体中央裂开了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,このままだと沈没する　早く脱出を
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.08,0:16:12.72,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这样下去船会沉的 快点出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,りょ…了解
Dialogue: 1,0:16:12.94,0:16:14.12,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,明…明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.29,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ミーナさんは脱出されました
Dialogue: 1,0:16:17.61,0:16:19.29,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们接回了明娜同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.49,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長は
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.64,0:16:20.49,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,まだ確認できておりません
Dialogue: 1,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.36,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,还没找到她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.05,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,その　連絡が…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:22.89,0:16:25.05,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,切れましたわ…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:25.05,0:16:26.54,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,联系不上她了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.41,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,怖いよな
Dialogue: 1,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.41,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你也很怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私も怖い
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.50,0:16:36.80,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我也很怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:40.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,何しろ私は運が悪いし
Dialogue: 1,0:16:36.92,0:16:40.72,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,因为我总是不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,このままじゃダメだ
Dialogue: 1,0:16:45.72,0:16:46.99,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不能坐着等死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,行こう
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.86,0:16:49.57,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.08,0:16:50.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長
Dialogue: 1,0:16:50.08,0:16:50.96,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:52.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長…
Dialogue: 1,0:16:51.39,0:16:52.24,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,シロちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.20,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,待ってるって　こんなに辛いんだね
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.99,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,等待原来这么痛苦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.27,0:17:04.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,でも…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.27,0:17:04.80,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.42,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,シロちゃんと約束したから
Dialogue: 1,0:17:05.82,0:17:07.42,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我和小白已经说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.85,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救助した人たちに毛布を
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.30,0:17:09.85,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,给避难人员发毛毯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.82,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,それから何か食べ物　暖かい飲み物を用意して
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.25,0:17:13.82,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,另外准备一些吃的 还有热饮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.76,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.92,0:17:14.76,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.33,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,みんな　いるよね
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.36,0:17:20.33,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,大家都还在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,航海科の子たちは？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.86,0:17:22.22,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,航海科的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救助した人と一緒に船に戻ったよ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.52,0:17:25.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,和避难人员一起回晴风号了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.88,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,後は副長だけ？
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.20,0:17:26.88,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,只剩副舰长一个了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長…
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.12,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ブルーマーメードだ
Dialogue: 1,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.12,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,是蓝色人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ブルーマーメード　保安即応艦隊の岸間です
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.22,0:17:43.26,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我是蓝色人鱼紧急响应舰队的岸间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:47.13,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,晴風　砲雷科　小笠原光以下救助隊です
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.48,0:17:47.13,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们是晴风号炮雷科的小笠原光救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.50,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ご苦労様　後は任せて
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.45,0:17:49.50,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,辛苦各位了 剩下的交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,まだ船内に一人学生が
Dialogue: 1,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.26,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,船上还有一个学生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.43,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 1,0:17:51.63,0:17:52.43,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.31,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要救助者一名
Dialogue: 1,0:17:54.06,0:17:55.31,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,救援对象 一人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,仕方ない
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.78,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.66,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,救助した人たちに食事は行き渡ってる？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:12.35,0:18:14.66,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,避难人员都吃上饭了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,怪我人がいたら報告して
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.57,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,有伤员的话报告给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.75,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お粥　いかがですか
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.78,0:18:18.75,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,喝粥吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お汁粉もありますよ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.02,0:18:20.86,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,还有年糕豆汤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.69,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,やっぱり　ついてない
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.16,0:18:33.69,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,还是这么不走运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.61,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,クソ
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.54,0:18:39.61,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:41.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,そっちはどう？
Dialogue: 1,0:18:40.92,0:18:41.96,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,那边怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,まだ反応みあた…
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.25,0:18:43.36,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,没有探测到…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.46,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ハンマー用意して
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.46,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,给我锤子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.96,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,艦長　救援艦より連絡
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.24,0:18:47.96,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,舰长 救援舰说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.14,0:18:52.94,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,現在ブルーマーメード隊が副長の捜索活動を行っているそうです
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.14,0:18:52.94,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,现在蓝色人鱼正在搜救副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,シロちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:18:53.44,0:18:54.40,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.43,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お腹空いた
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.73,0:19:02.43,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.24,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,要救助者　位置確認
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.59,0:19:10.24,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,发现救援对象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.14,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,周辺確認　問題なし
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.46,0:19:12.14,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,周边一切正常
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:14.62,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,聞こえる？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:13.72,0:19:14.62,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,能听见吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:17.20,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,そのまま動かないで　じっとしてて
Dialogue: 1,0:19:14.83,0:19:17.20,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,千万别乱动 我们马上进去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.86,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,助かったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.86,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.26,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,副長
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.28,0:19:25.26,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,副舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.40,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,怪我はない？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.31,0:19:28.40,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.65,0:19:29.55,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.65,0:19:29.55,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,よう生きとったのうわれ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.60,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,活着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,助かったにゃあ　よかったにゃあ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.45,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我们得救了喵 真是太好了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.54,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,なんで猫言葉になっとる？
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.54,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,为什么要学猫叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.80,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,多聞丸　無事救助しました
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.80,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,成功救出多闻丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.63,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.17,0:19:49.63,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:50.57,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,どうぞ
Dialogue: 1,0:19:49.79,0:19:50.57,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,给
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,多聞丸
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.01,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,多闻丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.51,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,多聞丸　行かないと
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.30,0:19:58.51,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,多闻丸 你该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.31,0:20:00.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,随分懐いてるな
Dialogue: 1,0:19:59.31,0:20:00.99,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,它很喜欢你嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,こら　多聞丸
Dialogue: 1,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,不行 多闻丸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.24,0:20:05.90,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,あの…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:05.24,0:20:05.90,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.22,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,よかったら
Dialogue: 1,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.22,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,要不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,面倒　見てもらえますか
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.65,0:20:10.64,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你来照顾它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.78,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ご迷惑でなければ
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.28,0:20:12.78,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,如果你不嫌弃的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:20.59,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お手数ですが　それを横須賀女子海洋学校まで届けてください
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.20,0:20:20.59,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,麻烦各位了 请把它转交横须贺女子海洋学校
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.27,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,了解しました
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.21,0:20:22.27,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.93,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,それと　これも
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.46,0:20:23.93,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,另外还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.33,0:20:24.99,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,これは？
Dialogue: 1,0:20:24.33,0:20:24.99,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,抗体と　私の報告書です
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.64,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,抗体及其个人使用报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.17,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ただいま
Dialogue: 1,0:20:29.16,0:20:30.17,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:31.98,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,シロちゃん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.97,0:20:31.98,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,小白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.77,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,よかった無事で
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.77,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,你没事就好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私　待ってる間ずっと苦しかった
Dialogue: 1,0:20:36.38,0:20:39.45,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我等你的时候一直很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.48,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,シロちゃんをずっとこんな…
Dialogue: 1,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.48,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,还以为会把你永远留在…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.48,0:20:44.01,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ごめんね　ごめんね
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.48,0:20:44.01,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.52,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,宗谷さん
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.52,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,宗谷同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.86,0:21:03.37,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,もう一匹　乗せてもいいだろうか　艦長
Dialogue: 1,0:20:58.86,0:21:03.37,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,船上能不能再挤一只？舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.34,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,もちろん
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.34,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.71,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,可愛い
Dialogue: 1,0:21:05.77,0:21:07.71,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:15.21,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,本職のブルマーはさすがだったな
Dialogue: 1,0:21:12.94,0:21:15.21,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,专业蓝人不愧是专业的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.53,0:21:18.60,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私も遭難した時助けてもらったから
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.53,0:21:18.60,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,以前我遇难的时候也被她们救过
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.92,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ブルーマーメードになろうと思ったんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.92,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以才想做蓝色人鱼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.87,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,それに船に乗れば　家族ができると思って
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.03,0:21:25.87,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,而且我觉得上了船以后 或许就能有家人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,私のお母さん　ブルーマーメードだったの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:26.65,0:21:29.47,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,我妈妈以前是蓝色人鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.48,0:21:34.36,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,お母さん言ってた　海の仲間は家族みたいなんだって
Dialogue: 1,0:21:30.48,0:21:34.36,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,她说 海上的伙伴们就像一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.64,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,だから　私もミケちゃんも　ブルーマーメードになったら
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.89,0:21:38.64,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以 我和明明成为蓝色人鱼之后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.72,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,たくさん家族ができると思うの
Dialogue: 1,0:21:38.70,0:21:40.72,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,肯定能得到一个大家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.32,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,だから　約束しようよ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.26,0:21:43.32,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以 我们做个约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:49.45,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,だからあんなに　海の仲間は家族だと
Dialogue: 1,0:21:45.72,0:21:49.45,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,所以你才总是说 海上的伙伴们都是一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.00,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,そのもえかという子が武蔵の艦長か
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.95,0:21:53.00,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,那个叫萌香的就是武藏号的舰长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:59.58,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,わしもうちの艦長　テアとは中学からずっと一緒じゃった
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.96,0:21:59.58,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,老夫和我们舰长西娅 也是初中以来的老交情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.45,0:22:05.47,TEXT-JP A-OTF Folk Pro B,,0,0,0,,ウイルスの抗体も出来たことじゃしな　早く助けに行きたい
Dialogue: 1,0:22:01.45,0:22:05.47,TEXT-CN 方正正准黑_GBK,,0,0,0,,病毒的抗体已经做好了 好想快点去救她
